profile_positions.description:
-	HR Manager for all entities (Graco, Rubbermaid Commercial Products, Irwin, Lenox, Parker, Waterman, and the Financial Shared Services Center Europe) in the Netherlands;
-	Negotiating employment contracts;
-	Develop and maintain effective employee relations and act as confidential representative;
-	Develop a partnership with managers to enable effective HR support and delivery of solutions;
-	Identify and implement mandatory changes;
-	Act as business partner/lead contact for any HR issues in the Netherlands;
-	Manage the salary administration;
-	Head of the safety Committee in the Netherlands;
-	Facility/Safety Manager Goirle; 
-	Daily administrative tasks (making contracts, updating salary administration, updating Cyborg, etc.);
-	Manage the employees from reception;
-	Support the EMEA HR Director in business development and strategy activities.
